{"tid":316217,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［軍師聯盟］公無渡河 公竟渡河 墜河而死 當奈公何","createTime":"2017-07-10T14:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T13:20:46.000Z","uid":18720,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d11ddbf2fbe0ef538f6613a044db110ef5acc8e","tid":316217,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"軍師聯盟猶勝琅琊榜<br />\n與同樣三國為題材既新三國可為平分秋色<br />\n省卻所有戰爭場面<br />\n鬥智權謀 計計相連 目不暇給<br />\n<br />\n難得既一套以魏國為主線既大作<br />\n司馬懿堪比德川家康<br />\n具王佐之才 奉二代雄才之下<br />\n一生如履薄冰 傳奇不輸帝王將相<br />\n<br />\n吳秀波老師演繹得極好<br />\n老實講 佢好多側面都好似偉仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同楊主簿相惜相爭相鬥 不失君子之風<br />\n<br />\n呢版曹操 同陳建斌老師版本互相輝映<br />\n霸氣、傲氣、帝王之氣不輸任何一代曹操 甚或連姜文都猶有不及<br />\n佢同文若既感情 最後既結局 令人惜之嘆之"},{"pid":"9a9dc4971795eb1de05a9f3cbedb4b53b0458436","tid":316217,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/223340_701f18efe79e0a78ec29142d718657c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F223340_701f18efe79e0a78ec29142d718657c2.jpg&h=ce7cd970&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a3d8f397d80f85f9246f8eb9b5154a0337159d6","tid":316217,"uid":18720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/223441_26946170af9fd7c08053e8879f0e2d88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F223441_26946170af9fd7c08053e8879f0e2d88.jpg&h=337769ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b90cf87ee6ec36fa36f7bb6c6b4a70f07cd6fada","tid":316217,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/223501_74f33ef30fc40d4ad97cafc3cbf608f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http