ji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n令君同崔炎既計中計真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dadc07d556ab776a7a027dfaffd9e3eee887d7","tid":316217,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曹操死後，成套劇打五折</blockquote><br />\n孟德死後 冇人壓場 變成一般宮廷劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e04960a313a0181b3643b3a01a435956347ae4b","tid":316217,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曹操麻麻播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲達同德祖就真係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曹操做得好立體wo，好仔細咁演繹出後期既曹操</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為曹操既角色定左個新高度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估唔到魏國奪嫡咁引人入勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba663ccd8be6bf788854e6806785c7b098eceefd","tid":316217,"uid":63888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"見咁多人讚就開始睇，真係唔錯，真係好難想像一個人可以同時演活劉備同曹操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446b7379c6ccc0583cdf50bf75b578827f0470cb","tid":316217,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見咁多人讚就開始睇，真係唔錯，真係好難想像一個人可以同時演活劉備同曹操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n于和偉老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難以想像佢將曹操演到咁神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb561e39dd13e3dc49e33af7c4bb226e9ed24b8","tid":316217,